I have come to admire a culture in which employees consistently strive to improve and better serve our customers. That commitment is reflected in the stories we hear from travellers about the professionalism and care shown by our teams.
I remain confident in VIA Rail’s ability to modernize responsibly, manage costs effectively and build a financially sustainable future for passenger rail in Canada. I thank our teams across the country for their dedication and professionalism, which make that progress possible.


 
